snippet.title: Nauka Prediel Trailer
snippet.description:
Inspector Vasily Bogdanov, this may be your last adventure. Make sure travelling to Novosibirsk was worth it. 

We are in 1970, the events detailed happened in the vecinities of Novosibirsk in an intergubernamental facility that an upcoming news reporter made "detective" has decided to cover. Reports from here detail that there have been unusual activities in an empty forest, isolated from the city.
